Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's because I never put a limit for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.94,0:11:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to but never managed to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as you said, I might have thought
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,of having a girlfriend as my own happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.22,0:11:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It can only be you, or else...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm saying is,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd still end up choosing you anyway, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I love you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:41.11,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Hiroko acted like we never met before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:43.28,Alternate,,0,0,0,,I stopped going to university.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:47.69,Alternate,,0,0,0,,I only go shopping for the bare\Nminimum I need for living.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.92,0:11:52.69,Alternate,,0,0,0,,And so, about what I have been doing lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on! Shoot it out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:12:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll feel relieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to come after holding it in as long as I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.57,0:12:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'll say something like that, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(247,455)}Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(247,455)}Three... Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(247,455)}Three... Two... One...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,See? You came!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, if you keep squeezing me that hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll come in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like your car is about to go off-course, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.83,0:12:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Even if you tell me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.31,0:12:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, you lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,One more round, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:51.25,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Each day passed by.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:55.35,Alternate,,0,0,0,,I indulged in my daily life where Nina\Nkeeps squeezing me dry of semen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:13:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, where have you been staying\Nbefore coming over here to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.06,0:13:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it was the room beneath, but we're on the ground floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Wanna go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.20,0:13:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you lift that flooring up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... So, even a rundown apartment like this
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,has a basement beneath this floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.41,0:13:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there was a different building here long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:35.53,Alternate,,0,0,0,,What is this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:39.30,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Huh, is that an urn?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:44.17,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Then, is that the portrait of\Nthe owner of the remains?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:46.67,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:48.17,Alternate,,0,0,0,,A letter?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.17,0:13:52.18,Textblock,,0,0,0,,{=0}{\an4\c&H243A4E&\fs18\pos(175,240)\fnHelveticaNeue LT 55 Roman}Dear Nina,\N\NFirst of all, it's been a while. As you already know,\NI had to suddenly leave our home. My illness took a turn\Nfor the worse and I had been brought to the hospital.\NI've been here in a room up until now, and I want to\Nat least leave something for you in the end,\Nso I had my mother write this letter for me.\N\NI've been sick ever since I was little. I barely had been able\Nto go to school, thus I never made any friends. That is why\Nmy parents gave you to me as a gift. Others might see\Nmy life as a short one, a life which amounted to nothing.\NEven so, I can say that this life is a happy one, for I was able\Nto meet you.\N\NThank you for giving me the honor of taking care of you.\NThank you for staying by my side.\N\NAnd lastly...\NMy parents granted this selfish wish of mine, so it seems that\NI'll be able to stay together with you again afterwards.\NI might not be able to talk to you anymore like I always used to,\Nbut we'll be together forever.\N\N{\1a&HFF&}-----------------------------------------------------------------{\1a}— Kiyo
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.17,0:13:52.18,Textblock,,0,0,0,,{=0}{\fscx100\p1\bord2\pos(360,240)\c&HB3C8D4&\3c&H6B7984&\alpha&H1E&}m 0 0 l 420 0 420 450 0 450
Dialogue: 2,0:13:49.34,0:13:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, didn't you tell me that your\Nprevious owner abandoned you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:13:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.82,0:14:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you never read this letter before?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.95,0:14:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't care less about some letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.66,0:14:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I was only able to move around freely
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.26,0:14:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,ever since I managed to take a human form.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:10.86,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Then this girl had no idea
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.86,0:14:14.53,Alternate,,0,0,0,,about how much her previous\Nowner might have loved her,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.53,0:14:18.44,Alternate,,0,0,0,,and how she passed away from an illness\Nand won't be able to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, you weren't abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This letter is proof of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No! That human abandoned me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.65,0:14:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She left me behind and have\Nlong forgotten about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And even now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.66,0:14:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She's somewhere out there, being carefree...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and living her own life!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.60,0:14:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason she never came back for me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is because she abandoned me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.04,0:14:55.74,Alternate,,0,0,0,,This girl didn't just easily decide by\Nherself that she was abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:15:00.25,Alternate,,0,0,0,,She truly believed on her owner\Nonly to have that faith betrayed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.68,0:15:04.78,Alternate,,0,0,0,,You never loved me, so you abandoned me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:07.42,Alternate,,0,0,0,,I'd rather be a miserable doll like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:09.66,Alternate,,0,0,0,,So please, if anything else...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:14.03,Alternate,,0,0,0,,I wish for you to live your life\Nsomewhere out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.63,0:15:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When the time for me\Nto leave this world comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.67,0:15:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,never again will I ever leave you alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,484)}We will be going together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, the two of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...will meet your previous owner over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a promise!
